    "Some of these studies provide early indications that the abstraction to natural language provides superior generalization and noise-robustness capabilities compared to more conventional deep-learning tools 43, 44.",
    "Nonetheless, ultimately these early studies replace artificial neural networks or other algorithms implementing a specific functionality by LFMs; the LFMs in refs.",
